# Enjaz Task Manager - Unified GitIgnore

# === Shared / General ===
node_modules/
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/

# === FrontEnd Specific ===
FrontEnd/node_modules/
FrontEnd/build/
FrontEnd/dist/
FrontEnd/coverage/
FrontEnd/.pnp/
FrontEnd/.pnp.js

# === BackEnd Specific ===
BackEnd/node_modules/
BackEnd/.env
BackEnd/*.log
BackEnd/uploads/

# === Misc ===
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
